data.description: You'll never want to leave when this is your next home! Incredible four-bedroom, two-bathroom ranch in the desirable Eagle Trace neighborhood (No HOA). Nestled in a large shady lot, this home offers privacy and space in a friendly, well-kept community. The cozy exterior and curb appeal is just the beginning - inside you'll find a tastefully designed open-concept living room that includes a vaulted great room with wood flooring, and ceiling fan. The upgraded, custom kitchen includes beautiful wood cabinetry, granite countertops, a statement range hood, and a newly installed backsplash. Enjoy a snack at the breakfast bar or sit down with the family in the dining nook. The owner's suite is tucked away from the rest of the bedrooms and includes an en suite bathroom with garden tub, double-sink vanity, separate shower, and convenient walk-in closet with shelving. Two additional bedrooms feature neutral d?cor, carpeting, and ceiling fans. The shared bathroom is completely up to date and includes a full tub/shower combo. The laundry room includes storage above the washer and dryer hookups. A bonus room located upstairs is carpeted and can be used as a fourth bedroom, study, home office, or kids' play area. A nice-sized wooden deck is located off the great room. It's perfect for entertaining, evening dinners with the family, or enjoying the privacy this backyard affords. A freshly installed dry creek bed offers visual appeal to the landscape. This home also includes an attached, two-car garage. Convenient to shopping, dining, and local schools - and with no HOA fees in this neighborhood - this perfect home is just waiting to welcome its new family.
